title: Ep46 Evil Twins
description: This week's fan-picked episode has the gals seeing double with an entire show about Evil Twins. Topics include an ancient cosmic egg, a resilient pair of Swedish nutcases, and some charming English rabble-rousers. Paired with this episode is Winc's Kin & Country Primitivo, so pour two glasses, set your gin trap, shave your goatee, and tune in.    This episode is supported by TalkSpace, the online therapy company that makes it easy to connect with an experienced, licensed therapist, hand-picked just for you. Use promo code GALS for $30 off your first month! #TreatYoBrain
